      <h1 class='title'>Income Distribution</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 cc39-40WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_39ws' title='Col. 39WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c39WS' name='column_39ws' href='#column_39ws' rel='bookmark'>39WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-04695'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_188'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-michael-meacher' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_188' title='Link to this speech by Mr Michael Meacher' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-michael-meacher" title="Mr Michael Meacher">Mr. Meacher</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-04695">To ask the Chancellor of the Exchequer what percentage of national income accrued to the<span class="italic">(a)</span> top and <span class="italic">(b)</span> bottom (i) 1 per cent, (ii) 5 per cent. (iii) 10 per cent. and (iv) 20 per cent. of the income distribution in each year since 1979. [134101]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
